des:
Six Word Stories are brief and powerful. Here are a collection of six word love stories made to inspire you, to express many of the messages of love. Each story is randomly selected each time for your repeated listening enjoyment.

Enjoy the powerful messages in six words. Play them with someone you love, or to inspire you to communicate meaningfully with that special person.
